collectionTitle: Secret Space Society: OG Club Cards
content: The Secret Space Society OG Club Cards entitle holders to exclusive rewards in the Secret Space Society. Owning a Club Card will allow the holder to have early access to the SSS DAO where experts will make SOL, Stock, and Sports betting calls. Holders will also receive 150 $SS upon Naut mint which is our main collection of 3,333 supply. Holders will also receive a 1.25 multiplier on each Naut staked (max 3). They will be guaranteed 2 mints at a reduced price by 0.5SOL on each Naut.
